data.description: BEAUTIFULLY UPGRADED One Level Home Located In Very Desirable TRADITIONS. 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, Approximately 1,944 Square Feet Of Living Area, 2-Car Direct Access Garage & Indoor Laundry Room. Property Features Include; Charming Covered Front Porch Entry, Comfortable Great Room That Has Vaulted Ceiling, Gorgeous Luxury Wood Style Plank Vinyl Flooring With Accent Baseboards, Elegant Fireplace With Beautiful Travertine Surround Wall & Sliding Door Access To Wonderful Patio/Back Yard. Open Kitchen With Premium Whirlpool Brand Appliances Including Gas Cooktop Stove/Oven, Beautiful Quartz Polished Stone Counter Tops With Decorative Backsplash, Breakfast Bar, Handsome Natural Wood Style Cabinetry, Pantry, Farmhouse Style Sink, Recessed Lighting & Separate Dining Area. Lovely Relaxing Bedrooms Including Larger Master Suite With Gorgeous Wood Style Plank Vinyl Flooring, Vaulted Ceiling, Attractive Paint Design, Spacious Walk-In Closet, Direct Access To Beautiful Back Yard & Patio And Luxurious Personal Bathroom. Almost $60,000 In Upgrades That Include; Premium Whirlpool Brand Kitchen Appliances & Washer/Dryer, ADA Height Toilets & Shower Heads, Patio Installation & Back Yard Landscaping, Dining Room Light Fixture, Quality Brand Interior Paint Throughout, Travertine Fireplace Facing And Wood Mantle, Quartz Kitchen Counter Tops With Backsplash, Farmhouse Sink, Luxury Flooring, Window Treatments, Backyard Fountain, Kitchen Knobs/Pulls, Opaque Bathroom Windows And Front Screen Door.
